text: Nicole Julianne Sullivan (born April 21, 1970 in Manhattan, New York) is an American actress and comedian. She is best known for doing sitcoms. She acted in the sketch comedy MADtv (1995 to 2001) and the CBS sitcom The King of Queens. == Animated series == *Buzz Lightyear of Star Command - Mira Nova, Feara *Baby Blues - Bizzy *Brandy And Mr. Whiskers - Gerri *Big Hero 6 - Stern Woman *Bojack Horseman - Tracy *Clone High - Joan, Marie Curie *DC Super-Hero Girls - Supergirl *Family Guy - Muriel *Harley Quinn - Mrs. Copplepot, Benjamin, Hostess *Kim Possible - Shego, Computer Voice, Tour Guide, Additional voices *Lilo & Stitch: The Series - Shego, Additional voices *Nutri Ventures - Purple Guga *Pepper Ann - Tundra Woman *Robotboy - Additional voices *Rugrats - Debbie *Slacker Cats - Louise *Spongebob Squarepants - Fish 45, Additional voices *Stanley - Farmer Julie *Super Best Friends Forever - Supergirl *Teamo Supremo - Fabrica *The Penguins of Madagascar - Marlene *The Powerpuff Girls (1998) - Mollie, Maggot, Additional Voices *The Powerpuff Girls (2016) - Additional voices *Spider-Man (2017) - Mother, Additional voices *The Secret Saturdays - Drew *The Loud House - Additional voices *The Super Hero Squad Show - Additonal voices *The Fairly OddParents - Additional voices *Triptank - Sarah, Caitlin ==References== ==Other websites== Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from New York City Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Manhattan
